---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Reunião Pública">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 px-4 overflow-hidden bg-brand-blue">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue via-brand-blueDark to-blue-900 opacity-90"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(255,255,255,0.05)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:24px_24px]"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-8">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-white/20 shadow-2xl bg-white flex items-center justify-center p-2 group hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500 text-brand-blue">
                <img src="/images/esclarecimento.png" alt="Logo Reunião Pública" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
            </div>
            <div class="text-white max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 rounded-full backdrop-blur-md mb-6 border border-white/20 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-100 shadow-sm">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path></svg>
                    Acolhimento Fraterno
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight drop-shadow-md">
                    Reunião Pública
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light">
                    Compreensão do Evangelho de Jesus à luz dos ensinamentos espíritas. Esclarecimento, consolo e esperança.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="py-24 px-4 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-16">
            
            <!-- O que é -->
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 text-brand-blue rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Sobre a Reunião</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    A <strong>Reunião Pública</strong> funciona com várias salas simultâneas, propiciando aos seus frequentadores a opção de escolha. Assim, dentre os temas oferecidos na noite, o frequentador busca o que mais lhe convier.
                </p>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    Os temas oferecidos são atuais e de interesse geral. Lições em torno dos problemas humanos são explicadas de maneira fácil, agradável e atraente. O Livro dos Espíritos e o Evangelho de Jesus são temas permanentes e estudados de forma sequenciada.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Cronograma -->
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 text-brand-blue rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Cronograma</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-xl shadow-gray-200/40">
                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Terça-feira</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 italic">Essa atividade é aberta para o público em geral que procura a casa espírita para assistir a uma palestra e receber o passe magnético.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="overflow-x-auto mt-8">
                        <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
                            <thead>
                                <tr class="bg-blue-50/50 border-b-2 border-brand-blue/10">
                                    <th class="py-4 px-6 font-bold text-gray-800 w-1/3 rounded-tl-xl">Horário</th>
                                    <th class="py-4 px-6 font-bold text-gray-800 rounded-tr-xl">Atividade</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
                                <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
                                    <td class="py-4 px-6 text-brand-blue font-semibold">19h30 às 20h00</td>
                                    <td class="py-4 px-6 text-gray-700">Recepção e encaminhamento às salas</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
                                    <td class="py-4 px-6 text-brand-blue font-semibold">20h00 às 20h40</td>
                                    <td class="py-4 px-6 text-gray-700">Reunião pública: palestra com temas diversos</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
                                    <td class="py-4 px-6 text-brand-blue font-semibold">20h40 às 20h45</td>
                                    <td class="py-4 px-6 text-gray-700">Deslocamento para a sala de passe</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
                                    <td class="py-4 px-6 text-brand-blue font-semibold">20h45</td>
                                    <td class="py-4 px-6 text-gray-700">Passe</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- YouTube CTA -->
            <div class="mt-24 bg-white rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-16 text-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-gray-100">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(0,0,0,0.02)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:16px_16px]"></div>
                <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 text-red-600 drop-shadow-sm" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"/></svg>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Transmissão Online</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-light leading-relaxed">
                        Acompanhe as palestras da Reunião Pública ao vivo pelo nosso canal do YouTube. Participe de onde estiver, toda terça-feira a partir das 20h!
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/user/osgept/live" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-10 py-5 bg-red-600 text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-full hover:bg-red-700 transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl shadow-xl group">
                        Assistir no YouTube
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path></svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
